'''Kirby's Adventure''' is a late-era NES platformer featuring Kirby's copy ability system for the first time.

==Overview==

One of the largest and most technically impressive NES games:
* First appearance of copy abilities
* 25 different copy abilities
* 7 worlds with multiple levels
* Mini-games and secrets
* Advanced NES graphics techniques

